{"tid":772094,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【懷念90年】4匪扑劫尖沙嘴找換店職員 搶走千萬現金","createTime":"2018-08-08T13:03:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T14:47:50.000Z","uid":136988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cce765d1422f49e9173c07e89db31dc4263a2d11","tid":772094,"uid":136988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T13:03:38.000Z","msg":"尖沙嘴發生千萬劫案，晚上7時許，中間道一名找換店男職員將一個公事篋擺上一部七人車時，3名賊人突然走近，從後用玻璃樽襲擊職員頭部，掠去該公事篋，消息稱公事篋內裝約值1千萬元現金，3名賊人得手後跳去一部接應的私家車絕塵而去。警方接報到場，正在附近一帶兜截疑犯。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解依家好似變番90年代成日有打劫"},{"pid":"5da49e5084d6978c856673c7fd77bdd3a0b40381","tid":772094,"uid":79077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:23:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c0c18ec8faf934000118be5923c871c76c53fc93","tid":772094,"uid":159794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:39:38.000Z","msg":"以前一千萬 新聞都要做幾日<br />\n<br />\n而加一角仔"},{"pid":"eaa5487eaae7451d918edf56fa92aac4cb0f6fac","tid":772094,"uid":22913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:44:29.000Z","msg":"咁撚易就搶到 全世界都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84ac4548d62cc7b2cd63cab7e856ce56e15bc308","tid":772094,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:47:50.000Z","msg":"省港旗兵&gt;<br />\n咖喱牛蝻"}]}